Reclusa::

She felt a little insulted at his comment. However, she could
understand security concerns. She nodded, "Very well."
She was getting a little annoyed about how things had been since she
was imprisoned in her cocoon. She was rather hoping the Maximals would
be only a small resistance and the Predacons be ruling the galaxy by
now. Her face plates showed a minor irritation as she felt her
disappointment in the Predacon process so far. However, she seemed to
give a small smile as she knew that since she was now here, things
would truely change for the better.  After all, her programs made her
a very accomplished killer and skilled planner.  She felt that she
would be a great asset to the Predacons.
